#: ../../source/index.rst:2
msgid "EDAI documentation"
msgstr "EDAI 文档"

#: ../../source/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"**EDAI** (Electronic Design Automation Intelligence) is an LLM-driven "
"terminal user interface for EDA tools. It combines an IPython shell "
"environment with a natural language agent to let you interact with EDA "
"tools using plain English, Tcl commands, or Python — all within a single "
"session."
msgstr ""
"**EDAI** (Electronic Design Automation Intelligence) 是一个由大语言模型驱动的 EDA 工具终端界面。"
"它将 IPython shell 环境与自然语言智能体相结合，让您可以在同一会话中通过英语、Tcl 命令或 Python 与 EDA 工具进行交互。"
